T1.value: Hindleg coxal process (MP) flat, base of hindleg trochanter (MT) free or nearly so; less than 2.4mm in length

T28.value: Scutellum not visible; small beetles length not greater than 6.3mm

T29.value: Scutellum visible; large beetles, length 5.4mm or greater

T3.value: Hindleg coxal process raised with sides covering base of hind leg trochanter; most specimens over 2.5mm in length

T31.value: Fore and middle leg tarsi with 5 distinct articles, 3rd and 4th articles of similar length

T33.value: Fore and middle leg tarsi with 4 articles, or with 5 articles but article 4 concealed by article 3

T7.value: Hindleg tibia (HLT) straight; hindleg tarsal claws (HC) unequal in length; body broad

T8.value: Hindleg tibia expanding towards apex; hindleg tarsal claws equal in length; elongate body
